                    <span>ABSOLUTELY RECOMMENDABLE for anyone interested in how the brain works. 
<br />The clear exposure and expertise of the author(s) makes of this book an extremely enjoyable read. 
<br />Great for Neuroscience and Cognitive science students. With citations supporting every little detail exposed, it creates a library for future readings. 
<br />For non-scientists interested in the brain and mind this book should be quite easy to understand.</span>
                  
              
